This bread was so easy to assemble, nutritious and tasty. I have made this on several occasions and everyone who tasted it raved about how good it was. I cooked this bread in a crock pot in the summer time so my kitchen will stay cool. The bread makes a great accompaniment to a traditional New England dinner.

