My mom makes this in her slow-cooker. Cooking times will vary widely -- test after 4 hrs.

Rating: 4
This is a delicious bread. Easy to prepare. The flavor and texture are great. The flavor of the molasses is just right and the corn meal adds body to the texture. I will make it again.